36:53.127 --> 36:55.295
It is an awesome sight.

36:55.463 --> 36:58.173
The giant spacecraft glinting...

36:58.341 --> 37:03.386
...in the Nevada sun like a giant...

37:03.554 --> 37:05.430
...hubcap.

