47:27.553 --> 47:30.805
The human race doesn't deserve to live.

47:37.604 --> 47:40.356
Ethel, that reminds me.

47:40.524 --> 47:43.150
I would like for every limo to be stocked...

47:43.318 --> 47:46.612
